    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。遊園地でのライブに向けて\n練習にも熱が入っているみたいだな",
      "startTime": 3.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "はい！\n……ただ、ちょっと不安なことがあるんです",
      "startTime": 9.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "今まではサニピの五人で支え合ってきたけど\n今回は私一人しかいないから……",
      "startTime": 18.6836687364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（そうか、場慣れしたさくらでも）\n（一人でパフォーマンス出来るか不安なんだな……）",
      "startTime": 25.3276191712,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "いつもは五人の掛け合いで笑いを取ってたから\n私一人のトークでちゃんとウケるか心配で……",
      "startTime": 32.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "確かにそれは心配だ……いや、待て待て！\nさくら？　アイドルは笑いを取らなくていいんだぞ？",
      "startTime": 40.8747393291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、トークでお客さんを盛り上げるのは\n大切なことだと思うんです",
      "startTime": 47.5948043209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "だから……当日までに手品を練習してきます！\nあと一輪車でバック走やります！",
      "startTime": 55.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "落ち着け、さくら\nそれはアイドルがライブでやることじゃないぞ",
      "startTime": 59.7210885367,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "あ……そ、そうですよね……\nなんだか私、空回りしてますね",
      "startTime": 67.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "一人で頑張らなきゃって\n少しプレッシャーを感じてるのかもしれません",
      "startTime": 75.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "私って、自分で思ってるよりずっと\nみんなに頼っていたんですね……",
      "startTime": 83.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに気負わなくても、さくらが普段通りの力を\n発揮すればライブはうまくいくさ",
      "startTime": 90.2863040927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "そう……ですよね……。分かりました！\n気合いを入れて、平常心で頑張ります！",
      "startTime": 98.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（平常心は頑張ってやることじゃないと思うが……）\n（まぁ、今はさくらを信じて見守るとしよう）",
      "startTime": 106.2517913185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "startTime": 111.0851246519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、聞いて下さい！\nどうしたら平常心でライブ出来るか考えてみたんです！",
      "startTime": 116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "いつも私は、サニピのみんながそばにいてくれるから\n安心して歌えるんです",
      "startTime": 124.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "つまり、みんなの存在を近くに感じられれば\n平常心で歌えるはずなんです",
      "startTime": 130.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……\nそれで具体的にどうするつもりだ？",
      "startTime": 134.066667684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたらみんなの存在を身近に感じられるか\nいろいろ考えて……閃いたんです",
      "startTime": 141.0999949138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "ライブ中に\n私がみんなのモノマネをすればいいんだって！",
      "startTime": 146.699975586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど………ん？\n今、変な提案が入らなかったか？",
      "startTime": 153.5557808244,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "それで今、みんなのモノマネを練習してるんです！\n今からやるので見てもらえませんか？",
      "startTime": 160.2666422527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "誰のモノマネか当ててみて下さい！\nいきますよ～！",
      "startTime": 166.0666422527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "――佐伯遙子、十七歳です！\nはぁ～、お酒が美味しいわ～",
      "startTime": 172.6857009575,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "どうですか？　誰のモノマネか分かりましたか？",
      "startTime": 177.4070275948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "第一声で名乗ってるじゃないか",
      "startTime": 181.599476497,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "今度は連続でいきますよ～\n誰のモノマネか当てて下さい！",
      "startTime": 186.6333089193,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-skr020.m4a",
      "text": "――今度、全米が恐怖で震えたというホラー映画を\n観に行きませんか？",
      "startTime": 194.1666422527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと待つんだ、さくら",
      "startTime": 196.2580479946,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_02-skr021.m4a",
      "text": "――アイドルショップ、行くとね……\n金銭感覚、故障する……",
      "startTime": 203.0201170594,
